sources.title: Swamp Rose (1961) Directed by Larry Buchanan - with Annabelle Weenick - 4K + Commentary
sources.description:
A rich old man, Shug, throws out his longtime live-in mistress and moves in his young niece, who's just returned home after making a living as a dancer in New Orleans. The mistress doesn't intend to go without a fight, however, and while Shug tries to make peace between the two women, he doesn't realize that his niece has her own plans for him.

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/cNDV_oUJyi0

Original title: Common Law Wife (1961)

Directors: Eric Sayers, Larry Buchanan
Producer: Fred A. Kadane
Starring: Annabelle Weenick, George Edgley, Lacey Kelly, Max W. Anderson
Genres: Hicksploitation, Drama
